OL,3,CMum of teen stabbed to death in Kent
OL,4,Csays she won't rest until she has
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FThe grieving mother of a teenager
OL,8,Fstabbed to death in Kent has said she
OL,9,Fwon't rest until she has justice for
OL,10,Fson Ashton.
OL,12,F19-year-old father, Ashton Harrington,
OL,13,Fwith stab wounds just after 2am on
OL,14,FFriday 3 April in Belmont Road,
OL,15,FWhitstable. He died at the scene.
OL,17,FTwo men have been arrested in
OL,18,Fconnection with his death this
OL,19,Fafternoon (Monday 13 April).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
