OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776103864
OL,3,CMum of teen stabbed to death in Kent
OL,4,Csays she won't rest until she has
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,F'Our officers have been seen across
OL,8,FSittingbourne, Herne Bay and Ramsgate
OL,9,Fas part of the investigation. We have
OL,10,Freceived really good support from the
OL,11,Fpublic and we would like to thank
OL,12,Fthem."
OL,14,FAshton leaves behind his mum Camille,
OL,15,Fstepdad Conor, grandmother Lorraine
OL,16,Fand brothers Bentley and Caisley who
OL,17,Fare 12 and 11 years old.
OL,19,FAshton's mum said she'll cherish the
OL,20,Flast message he sent her telling her
OL,21,Fhe loved her.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1776103864
OL,3,CMum of teen stabbed to death in Kent
OL,4,Csays she won't rest until she has
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FShe described Ashton as the 'life and
OL,8,Fsoul of the party', someone who loved
OL,9,Fsocialising and spending time with his
OL,10,Ffriends.
OL,12,FFollowing his death, flowers and
OL,13,Fmessages have been left close to the
OL,14,Fscene, including at the entrance to
OL,15,FWhitstable Town Football Club.
OL,17,FFour further arrests have been made as
OL,18,Fofficers continue to investigate his
OL,19,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
